{"tid":875210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果香港轉左軚","createTime":"2018-10-24T17:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T08:55:01.000Z","uid":71207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b8aedf349b84418e8b3b894f973e1bb9d179b3c","tid":875210,"uid":71207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T17:46:42.000Z","msg":"首先要屌一屌究竟邊條撚樣提出黎<br />\n依家香港仲唔夠麻煩？ 淨係條港鐵都搞到粒粒亂<br />\n 如果轉既話 其實基本好似冇乜可能(係香港黎講)<br />\n影響大到不得之了<br />\n第一 係香港行得既車基本上要換哂<br />\n第二 巴士路線 大改 鐵路改 例如輕鐵 得左邊有門 月台一定係輕鐵左邊<br />\n第三 所有路既線 燈<br />\n屌仲有好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純粹想大力屌屌今日提出呢個on9建議既人 <br />\n條友真係冇撚腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f9c2a1faf64605eb6139978ebb19ea7fa8d19a","tid":875210,"uid":71207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T17:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8528b6ce2cd423c88dff5dd89f756853c457136","tid":875210,"uid":68047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T17:56:37.000Z","msg":"屌得好"},{"pid":"938d176c0b7b749d9a216f4f3338abdea0c04253","tid":875210,"uid":8619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2bfa8e113597d5d3788c85b71d3e69d7ef53f4","tid":875210,"uid":71207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"938d176c0b7b749d9a216f4f3338abdea0c04253","tid":875210,"uid":8619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"